        "jsonBody": "={{ JSON.stringify({ model: 'claude-sonnet-4-20250514', max_tokens: 2000, messages: [{ role: 'user', content: 'You are a cybersecurity expert and professional educator who shares insights on LinkedIn.\\n\\nAnalyze the following educational content and create a concise LinkedIn post with this exact structure:\\n\\n1. TITLE - A bold, attention-grabbing headline\\n2. THESIS - One sentence stating your main argument or insight\\n3. EXAMPLES - 1-2 brief supporting examples or evidence (keep each to one sentence)\\n4. KEY POINTS - 2-3 bullet points using the \\u2022 character as bullets\\n5. QUESTION - End with one thought-provoking question for engagement\\n6. HASHTAGS - 3-5 relevant hashtags on their own line\\n\\nRules:\\n- Total post must be 50-80 words (excluding hashtags)\\n- Use plain text only - NO markdown formatting (no **, no ##)\\n- Use \\u2022 for bullet points\\n- Use line breaks to separate sections\\n- Be direct and punchy, not verbose\\n- IMPORTANT: Avoid repeating topics from previous posts. Previous post topics: ' + $json.pastTopics + '\\n\\nRespond with ONLY the LinkedIn post text. No JSON, no code blocks, no labels like \"TITLE:\" or \"THESIS:\". Just the post content.\\n\\nSource file: ' + $json.fileName + '\\n\\nSource content:\\n' + $json.content }] }) }}",
